disclaimer.title: Learn how reviews work
disclaimer.subtitle: Reviews from past guests help our community learn more about each home. By default, reviews are sorted by relevancy. Relevancy is based on recency, length, and information that you provide to us, such as your booking search, your country, and your language preferences. Only the guest who booked the reservation can leave a review, and Airbnb only moderates reviews flagged for not following our policies. To be eligible for a percentile ranking or guest favorite label, listings need at least 5 reviews in the last 4 years. Criteria is subject to change. Learn more in our Help Center

Haven View Retreat is located in White Haven/Freeland, in the heart of the Pocono Mountains.

Driving: Easily accessible via I-80 and I-476 (PA Turnpike), just minutes from White Haven.

Closest Airports: Wilkes-Barre/Scranton International Airport (~30 min), Lehigh Valley International Airport (~1 hr).

Parking: Free on-site parking for multiple vehicles.

EV Charging Available: A ChargePoint HomeFlex Level 2 EV Charger (J1772 connector) is available on-site for guest use. Tesla owners are welcome to charge using their J1772-to-Tesla adapter (not provided).
